  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Barnacle Nigiri</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Barnacle Nigiri</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> recipe exclusive to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i> introduced in <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Return_of_Them\" title=\"Return of Them\">Return of Them</a></i>. It is made of 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacles\" title=\"Barnacles\">Barnacles</a>, 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kelp_Fronds\" title=\"Kelp Fronds\">Kelp Fronds</a> and 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\">Eggs</a>.\n</p><p>Only Raw and Cooked Kelp Fronds are accepted. Using <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dried_Kelp_Fronds\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dried Kelp Fronds\">Dried Kelp Fronds</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacle_Pita\" title=\"Barnacle Pita\">Barnacle Pita</a> instead.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacle\" title=\"Barnacle\"><img alt=\"Barnacle.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Barnacle.png?1784c4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kelp_Frond\" title=\"Kelp Frond\"><img alt=\"Kelp Frond.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Kelp_Frond.png?a42104\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\"><img alt=\"Eggs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Eggs.png?a3e7ca\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacle_Nigiri\" title=\"Barnacle Nigiri\"><img alt=\"Barnacle Nigiri.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Barnacle_Nigiri.png?d2ef69\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/32px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacles\" title=\"Barnacles\"><img alt=\"Barnacles.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Barnacles.png?464354\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kelp_Fronds\" title=\"Kelp Fronds\"><img alt=\"Kelp Fronds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Kelp_Fronds.png?cb9519\" widt