"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacle_Nigiri\" title=\"Barnacle Nigiri\"><img alt=\"Barnacle Nigiri.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Barnacle_Nigiri.png?d2ef69\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacles\" title=\"Barnacles\"><img alt=\"Barnacles.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Barnacles.png?464354\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kelp_Fronds\" title=\"Kelp Fronds\"><img alt=\"Kelp Fronds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Kelp_Fronds.png?cb9519\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Egg\" title=\"Egg\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Egg.png?60f33e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Egg\" title=\"Egg\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Egg.png?60f33e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacle_Nigiri\" title=\"Barnacle Nigiri\"><img alt=\"Barnacle Nigiri.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Barnacle_Nigiri.png?d2ef69\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Barnacle Nigiri was introduced in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Return_of_Them#Troubled_Waters\" title=\"Return of Them\">Troubled Waters</a></i> update.</li></ul>\n<div></div>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacle_Nigiri#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacle_Nigiri#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
